\c 37
\s Vanhu vaJehovha vachamutswa samapfupa akaoma
\p
\v 1 Ruoko rwaJehovha rwakange ruri pamusoro pangu, akandibudisa noMweya waJehovha, akanondiisa pakati pomupata; iwo wakange uzere namafupa;
\v 2 akandipfuudza napakati pawo kumativi ese; tarirai, aivapo akawanda kwazvo pakachena pamupata; uye tarirai, akange akaoma kwazvo.
\v 3 Akati kwandiri: Mwanakomana, mapfupa awa angararama here? Ndikapindura, ndikati: Imi Ishe Jehovha munozviziva.
\p
\v 4 Zvino akatizve kwandiri: Porofita pamusoro pamapfupa awa, uti kwaari: Imi mapfupa akaoma, inzwai shoko raJehovha.
\v 5 Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha kumapfupa awa: Tarirai, ndichapinza mweya mukati menyu, muchararamazve.
\v 6 Ndichaisa marunda pamusoro penyu, nokuuisa nyama pamusoro penyu, nokukufukidzai neganda, nokuisa mweya mukati menyu, murarame; zvino muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha.
\p
\v 7 Ipapo ndakaporofita sezvandakarayirwa; zvino ndakati ndichiporofita, mubvumo ukavapo, uye, tarira, kudengenyeka kwenyika kwakavapowo; mapfupa akaswederana, ppfupa rimwe kune rimwe ppfupa raro.
\v 8 Ndikatarira, wane marunda avapo pamusoro pawo, nyama ikauya, ganda rikaafukidza pamusoro payo; asi makange musina mweya mukati mawo.
\v 9 Ipapo akati kwandiri: Porofitira kumhepo, porofita, mwanakomana womunhu, uti kumhepo: Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Uya uchibva kumativi mana anobva mhepo, iwe mweya, ufuridzire pamusoro pavava vakaurawa, kuti vararame.
\v 10 Ipapo ndakaporofita sezvaakandirayira, mweya ukapinda mukati mavo, vakararama, vakamira netsoka dzavo, iri hondo huru kwazvo.
\p
\v 11 Zvino akati kwandiri: Mwanakomana womunhu, mapfupa awa ndiyo imba yese yaIsraeri. Tarira ivo vanoti, mapfupa edu aoma, tariro yedu yaenda, taparadzwa chose.
\v 12 Naizvozvo porofita, uti kwavari zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Tarirai, ndichazarura marinda enyu, ndichakukwidzai mubve mumarinda enyu, imwi vanhu vangu; ndichakusvitsai munyika yaIsraeri.
\v 13 Muchaziva kuti ndini Jehovha, kana ndazarura marinda enyu, ndikakukwidzai mubve mumarinda enyu, imwi vanhu vangu.
\v 14 Ndichaisa mweya wangu mukati menyu, murarame, ndichakuisai munyika yenyu; zvino muchaziva kuti ini Jehovha ndakazvitaura ndikazviita, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\p
\v 15 Shoko raJehovha rakasvikazve kwandiri, richiti:
\v 16 Zvino iwe, mwanakomana womunhu, tora rutanda rumwe, unyore pamusoro parwo, kuti: ZvaJudha, nezvavana vaIsraeri shamwari dzake; ipapo utore rumwe rutanda, unyore pamusoro parwo, kuti: ZvaJosefa, rutanda rwaEfuremu, nezveimba yese yaVaIsraeri shamwari dzake;
\v 17 zvino uzvibatanidzire matanda iwawo, ruve rutanda rumwe, ruve rumwe muruoko rwako.
\p
\v 18 Zvino kana vana vavanhu vako vakataura newe vachiti kwauri: Haungatizivisi zvaunoda kuratidza nezvinhu izvi here?
\v 19 Iwe uti kwavari: Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Tarirai, ndichatora rutanda rwaJosefa, ruri muruoko rwaEfuremu, namarudzi aIsraeri shamwari dzake; ndichavaisa kwaruri, kurutanda rwaJudha, ndivaite rutanda rumwe, vachaita rumwe muruoko rwangu.
\p
\v 20 Zvino matanda aunonyora pamusoro pawo anofanira kuva muruoko rwako vazvione.
\v 21 Ipapo uti kwavari: Zvanzi naIshe Jehovha: Tarirai, ndichabvisa vana vaIsraeri pakati pamarudzi, kwavakaenda, ndichavaunganidza vabve kumativi ese, ndivaise kunyika yavo;
\v 22 ndichavaita rudzi rumwe panyika, pamakomo aIsraeri; mambo umwe uchava mambo wavese, havangazovi marudzi maviri, uye havangatongozovi ushe huviri hwakaparadzana;
\v 23 havangazozvisvibisi nezvifananidzo zvavo, kana nezvinhu zvavo zvinosemesa, kana nechinhu chipi nechipi chavanodarika nacho; asi ndichavaponesa pese pavagere, pavaitadza, nokuvanatsa; saizvozvo vachava vanhu vangu, neni ndichava Mwari wavo.
\v 24 Muranda wangu Dhavhidhi achava mambo wavo; vese vachava nomufudzi mumwe; vachafambawo nezvandakarayira, nokuchengeta mitemo yangu, vachiita.
\v 25 Vachagara munyika yandakapa Jakove muranda wangu, maigara madzibaba enyu; vachagaramo, ivo navana vavo, navana vavana vavo, nokusingaperi; Dhavhidhi muranda wangu achava muchinda wavo nokusingaperi.
\v 26 Ndichaitawo sungano yorugare navo, ichava sungano isingaperi navo; ndichavaisapo, nokuvawanza, nokuisa nzvimbo yangu tsvene pakati pavo nokusingaperi.
\v 27 Tabhenakeri yanguvo ichava pakati pavo; ini ndichava Mwari wavo, naivo vachava vanhu vangu.
\v 28 Zvino marudzi achaziva kuti ndini Jehovha, anoita VaIsraeri vatsvene, kana nzvimbo yangu tsvene iri pakati pavo nokusingaperi.